BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Fox Archives Day
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260823T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260823T180000
DTSTAMP:20260707T014648Z
UID:occ-1320@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Heritage Exhibition
DESCRIPTION:The Fox opens its archives — artifacts and archival material
 s from the 1929 movie palace\, with Atlanta History Center.\n\nThe fifth a
 nnual open house of the Fox Theatre's archives\, presented with the Atlant
 a History Center. Archival materials\, artifacts\, and exhibits trace the 
 building's story\, from 1929 movie palace to the grassroots campaign that 
 saved it from demolition in the 1970s. The displays fill the Grand Salon a
 nd Egyptian Ballroom\, so browsing doubles as a look inside two of the the
 atre's ornate event spaces.
GEO:33.7726136;-84.3853395
LAST-MODIFIED:20260707T013014Z
LOCATION:Fox Theatre\, 660 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://foxtheatre.evenue.net/cgi-bin/ncommerce3/SEGetEventList?groupC
 ode=ARC&linkID=fta&shopperContext=&caller=&appCode=
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Hamilton
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260902T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260902T220000
DTSTAMP:20260707T014648Z
UID:occ-1321@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Lin-Manuel Miranda's hip-hop biography of Alexander Hamilton\,
  on national tour.\n\nLin-Manuel Miranda's musical about Alexander Hamilto
 n\, the orphaned immigrant who wrote his way into the American Revolution 
 and the founding of the nation. The score moves through hip-hop\, R&B\, an
 d jazz\, drawing on Ron Chernow's biography for its history. Winner of 11 
 Tony Awards and the Pulitzer Prize for Drama\, with direction by Thomas Ka
 il and choreography by Andy Blankenbuehler. A national touring production.
GEO:33.7726136;-84.3853395
LAST-MODIFIED:20260707T013014Z
LOCATION:Fox Theatre\, 660 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://foxtheatre.evenue.net/cgi-bin/ncommerce3/SEGetGroupList?groupC
 ode=HAM&linkID=fta&shopperContext=&caller=&appCode=
END:VEVENT
